Analyzed:
Total sales and profit

Profit trends by year and category

Sales performance by product category

Top customers by revenue

Monthly sales trends

Customer count by year

Sales distribution across states

Data Visualization

Designed an interactive Sales & Profit Dashboard Used charts and KPIs to present insights clearly and intuitively

Included slicers for Category, Year, and Month to allow dynamic exploration

